      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，我先把主链路画出来：起点→validating→scheduled→awaiting_approval，审批确认后到executing。那executing执行完之后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
